<plot>Paper Dreams is an imaginative comedy for all ages about a lonely twelve-year old boy who fantasizes about being a hero. David has no friends, no interest in school, and a difficult home life. Instead, he finds peace of mind by playing with paper airplanes and imagining beating up two local school bullies. When he saves an oddball girl from the clutches of the troublemakers, he begins to experience friendship for the very first time. But when the bullies seek their revenge, David is forced to realize that he cannot always hide from his problems and the real world isn't made of fairy tale endings.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?422486</url></doc>
